February 24th

Good sheds with the workers at the shift lunch that take the motion controla war talking in particular on the one hand also of the question/price increase, a worker said "d _o so many years here I would be entitled to be able to go with my wife to eat occasionally Pizza, I can't do it because wages are not enough. And I also have to live an adult daughter who to study in the north alone cannot be it ... I have not voted for years but with this government it is still worse_ ", but good of the speeches are Also centered on the umpteenth grave incidental the day before to a young worker who risked losing a Hungamba, several workers denounced the fact that even if in part the security rules are the problem are the increasingly faster working times that at risk at risk In the movements etc., the confederals on this make unlawed little, sharing the question that the money must now serve for this more and more for the Guerr A and less and less for work, security, school, healthcare ...

