_Af en kommentator for Tjen Folket Media_

I den seneste uge har Folkehæren (NPA), led by the Filipino Communist Party, carried out several actions. This is reported by Angbayan, the newspaper affiliated with the party.

On February 15th, the Folk Army attacked(NPA)The old state's forces in the Albay region with remote controlled explosives.

A Lieutenant and 2 Soldiers from the Old State Army 49. Infantry Battalion were killed during the attack. The red soldier Eric Veraquit(In Nene)became martyr in the case of action.

16 \. February. A soldier from 94. Infantry battalion was killed in single -shooting operation performed by NPA in southern central Negros.

20 \. February. Two soldiers from the 31st infantry battalion were early Monday the morning attack and killed by red partisans while buying supplies at the local market in Barangay Cotmon. The two soldiers were part of a unit that had the task of ensuring the security of a controversial infrastructure project in the region. The Partisans conquered a gun of caliber 45 from the soldiers.

In the wake of the attack, the bourgeois media has tried to produce the occasional attack on soldiers who were on shopping and that the reason why Devar in the area was to initiate a search for a crashed aircraft.

To this end, a spokesman for the People's Army has stated that the soldiers were armed, dade was attacked and that it is not a bad thing to interrupt enemy supply lines, but on the contrary an excellent thing. The spokesman states that 31. IB is an active unit involved in Counter Guerilla operations and that it has been responsible for a series of people's rights and war crimes.

The spokesman concludes that the army army's armed operations in Albay show that the army army increases and strengthens his activities in these areas. It shows NPA ability to deploy and attack military targets anytime and anywhere.

